<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        .border {
            border: 3px solid #000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 5px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        p {
            text-align: justify;
            width: 85%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        table {
            width: 85%;
            margin: auto;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        th, td {
            border: 1px solid #000;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .table-active {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        small {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="border">
        <h2>Profilling Records Relating to a Deceased Person<br />(under the subject
            provisions of the Access to Unknown Act 1990)</h2>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Earum blanditiis odit libero
            officiis esse dicta non, aut aspernatur pariatur, voluptate soluta, quod quia ipsum a culpa? Sint pariatur,
            velit officia sed tempora, debitis cupiditate a hic enim molestias dolor quia quae consectetur excepturi odit,
            at aliquam! Cum error soluta nesciunt!</p>
        <table>
            <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Fullname</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.fullname %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Date of Death</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.deathDate %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Place of Death</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.placeDeath %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Birthdate</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.birthDate %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Place of Birth</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.placeBirth %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Age of Death</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.ageDeath %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Gender</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.gender %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Occupation</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.occupation %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Civil Status</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.civilStatus %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Religion</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.religion %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Citizenship</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.citizenship %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Cause of Death</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.causeDeath %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="table-active" style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">Name of Cemetery</td>
                    <td style="text-align: center;"><%= deceased.nameCemetery %></td>
                </tr>
            </tbody>
        </table>
        <small>ID:<%= deceased._id %>.doc</small>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
